MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 772

AMENDING PROCLAMATION NO. 483 DATED OCTOBER 28, 1968, WHICH RESERVED A PARCEL OF LAND LOCATED IN POBLACION, TAGUM CITY FOR CHILDREN’S PARK AND PLAYGROUND PURPOSES BY GRANTING OWNERSHIP OF THE SAME IN FAVOR OF THE CITY GOVERNMENT OF TAGUM

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by the virtue of the powers vested in me by the law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby amend Proclamation No. 483 dated October 28, 1968, which reserved a parcel of land located in Poblacion, Tagum City for children’s park and playground purposes by granting ownership of the same in favor of the City Government of Tagum, subject to private rights, if any there be, which parcel of land is more particularly described as follows:

LOT 1330, CAD 276

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 1330, Cad 276, Tagum Cadastre), located in Poblacion, Tagum City, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the NE., along line 10-11 by Lot 485; on the SE., along line 11-12 by Lot 396; along line 12-1 by Lot 397, all of Cad-276; on the SW., along lines 1-2-3 by Municipal Road; and on the NW., along lines 3-4-5-6-7-8-9-10 by Lot 485, Cad-276. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being S. 82 deg. 14′ E., 399.21 m. from BLLM No. 2, Cad-276, Tagum Cadastre, thence:

52.55 m. to point 2;

40.07 m. to point 3;

72.59 m. to point 4;

36.73 m. to point 5;

19.90 m. to point 6;

30.75 m. to point 7;

21.19 m. to point 8;

49.30 m. to point 9;

48.21 m. to point 10;

58.61 m. to point 11;

97.34 m. to point 12;

134.67 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of Thirteen Thousand Eight Hundred Forty Eight (13,848) square meters, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground by Old Points. Bearings true. Date of Survey April 1935 to May 1938 by Geodetic Engineer P. Nicdao.

The tract of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable nor be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease or any other mode of disposition until again declared by proclamation of the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 28th day of January, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

Reference: Special Patent No. 3656

